name: swan song
description:
weightlessness. universal emptiness, in which there is a place for everything and there is no place for anything at the same time.
act with complete faith, even if the moment requires you to leap empty-handed into the void. emptiness is the end. emptiness is the beginning.
this photo is a self-portrait, created in the moment of leaping into the void, after which the dawn came ...
do what makes your soul shine.
